      "content": "rebuild? how? there's no rebuilding from this. it's not just money, it's the shame. it's the way everybody looks at me like i'm some kind of joke/failure. i feel like if i just disappeared, the shame would just... stop. like the debt and the disappointment would just go away with me. everything feels so permanent and heavy. i just want the weight to be gone.",
